While working on the simple find widget I came across many instances of the misspelling. "focussed"
Most are in context key object names, however, there is one public facing instance, a context key
value that would appear in when clauses for key bindings.
I'm sure you do not want a PR for one hundred files ;-)

From: findController.ts

export const CONTEXT_FIND_WIDGET_VISIBLE = new RawContextKey<boolean>('findWidgetVisible', false);
export const CONTEXT_FIND_WIDGET_NOT_VISIBLE: ContextKeyExpr = CONTEXT_FIND_WIDGET_VISIBLE.toNegated();
export const CONTEXT_FIND_INPUT_FOCUSSED = new RawContextKey<boolean>('findInputFocussed', false);
